description: Returns complete information about the current rules and alerting logging configuration of the workspace.

parameters.name: workspaceId
parameters.description: The ID of the workspace to describe the logging configuration for.

nested_items.name: loggingConfiguration
nested_items.description: A structure that displays the information about the logging configuration.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the logging configuration was created.

nested_items.name: logGroupArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the CloudWatch log group to which the vended log data will be published.

nested_items.name: modifiedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the logging configuration was most recently changed.

nested_items.name: statusCode
nested_items.description: The current status of the current rules and alerting logging configuration.

nested_items.name: statusReason
nested_items.description: If failed, the reason for the failure.

nested_items.name: workspace
nested_items.description: The ID of the workspace the logging configuration is for.
